  <FactionDef ParentName="RH_FactionBase_MSF">
    <defName>RH_MSF</defName>
    <label>private military company</label>
    <description>Militaires Sans Frontières, abbreviated MSF and known in English as Army Without Borders, was a private military company founded and led by renowned mercenary Big Boss in the early 1970s. Abandoning their home countries, the "soldiers without borders" provided their services to all clients, regardless of nation or ideology, operating from their offshore Mother Base in the Caribbean Sea.

After leaving the Patriots in 1972, Naked Snake, a.k.a. Big Boss, formed the Militaires Sans Frontières to provide military force to anyone who needed it, regardless of nation or ideology. As such, the MSF specialized in providing a full range of military services, including combat, logistics, training, weapons, outfitting, and R&amp;D. In addition, the MSF was designed to merge the small footprint and exceptional performance of special forces groups with the full military might of a full regular army, as a means to fully break free of nation-states. To avoid enemy intelligence services like the CIA, MSF did not initially establish a permanent base, often choosing to relocate their forces as required.

They're friendly around small settlements in the hopes of finding customers, willing to offer a helping hand to those who might not even be able to afford their services under the reason of just being there for those who need an army without borders. If there's anything MSF does not like, it's a Nuclear Inspection.</description>
